document.topic_text: Pa abona EXTRA.CW klik riba e link aki. 2016-08-11 / Mundu Deportivo Print extra Little League Lesadónan di Extra Little League, bon dia. Nos tei bèk ku kolumna di Little League ku selekshon di Kòrsou Liga Pariba rumbo pa Williamsport. Awel… ta hopi kontentu mes e muchanan, coachnan i mayornan ta, ku nan ta rumbo pa Williamsport. * * * * *
